com.here.mobility.sdk.core.geo

Class GeoPolyline

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.mobility.sdk.core.geo.GeoPolyline
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Parcelable

    public final class GeoPolyline
extends Object
implements Parcelable
    A polyline over LatLng, that describes a path on the planet. The list of locations is ordered according to the path, from the first location to the last.

      • GeoPolyline

        public GeoPolyline(List<? extends HasLatLng> located)
        Creates a new GeoPolyline from the given list of located objects. Note that only the LatLng objects themselves, as returned by HasLatLng.getLatLng() are stored (in a new list).
